Steps followed:
1) add page.('/dist') to foo/routing.html 
```javascript
 window.addEventListener('WebComponentsReady', function() {
    page.base('/dist');
   ....
   });
```
2) gulp
3) python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000 dist/

Results:
1) navigate to http://localhost:8000/dist/ -> everything looks fine
2) click "home" -> URL changes to http://localhost:8000/ and page displays directory listing
3) click browser back button -> URL changes to http://localhost:8000/dist/ & page again looks fine
4) click "users" -> URL changes to http://localhost:8000/users and error code 404 displayed
5) same behavior for menu "contact"

